47:  * {@link org.apache.kafka.clients.consumer.CooperativeStickyAssignor}. Sticky assignors are rack-aware.
48:  * If racks are specified for consumers, we attempt to match consumer racks with partition replica
49:  * racks on a best-effort basis, prioritizing balanced assignment over rack alignment. Previously
50:  * owned partitions may be reassigned to improve rack locality. We use rack-aware assignment if both
51:  * consumer and partition racks are available and some partitions have replicas only on a subset of racks.
52:  */
